&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sales Manager – U.S. Refining (Fenceline Solutions)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ROLE TYPE:&amp;nbsp; I&lt;/strong&gt;ndividual Contributor (no direct reports)&lt;/p&gt;
